---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Contact — Trove Collections" topDisclosure={false}>
  <h1>Contact</h1>

  <p class="lede">
    The fastest way to reach us is email:
    <a href="mailto:hello@trovecollections.com">hello@trovecollections.com</a>.
  </p>

  <p>
    We read every message. Reply times depend on flight schedules — sometimes
    same day, sometimes a couple of days. If it's about a specific item, mention
    the product name and we'll get back to you with whatever context we have.
  </p>

  <h2>Press &amp; partnerships</h2>
  <p>
    Same email — please put <code>Press</code> or <code>Partnership</code> in the
    subject line and we'll route it accordingly.
  </p>

  <h2>Mailing address</h2>
  <p class="muted">
    Trove Collections, LLC<br />
    (mailing address available on request)
  </p>
</Layout>

<style>
  .lede {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    max-width: 60ch;
  }
  p { max-width: 65ch; }
  code {
    background: #F1E9DC;
    padding: 0.1rem 0.4rem;
    border-radius: 3px;
    font-size: 0.9em;
  }
</style>
